2. **No DOM test infrastructure**: `SettingsPage.tsx`'s notification toggle interaction (`setNotificationsEnabled` when clicked) can only be verified via source-level string assertion (checking the JSX has the correct wiring), not through DOM interaction. This matches the project's existing pattern.
